{"tid":1662340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動post］1020 九龍見，準備開始全力推post","createTime":"2019-10-18T16:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T11:10:55.000Z","uid":41366,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a21cc34b3eec35d727cfe11993fc5fdc09b95d","tid":1662340,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1020香港人全民召集<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/18/222059_10967b4045cae79ea56bc8beb1bdfbfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F18%2F222059_10967b4045cae79ea56bc8beb1bdfbfc.png&h=564f4b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位和理非，冇不反+蒙面法嘅情況下你地可能會驚<br />\n但謹記 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人多就最安全</span></strong></span>我哋去到今時今日，國際都開始注意我哋，係一班被捕，死去既手足，同仲有唔同戰線既前線手足爭取返嚟嘅成果，連遊行都唔敢出，憑咩叫口號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">要記住<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋約定係煲底一齊除口罩見面</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1020九龍見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vrqZu6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvrqZu6x.jpg&h=8abbb07e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe282b5a27d38b2f86f2afed14bda856886b051d","tid":1662340,"uid":7327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:52:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"350ba1a24c3d58e82c07505547bee494f952184f","tid":1662340,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【日常文宣】[推爆佢]本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f342a8e2d0ee20a2582046960f4669d89a73b77","tid":1662340,"uid":73157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be8e4ad27d1f4f249398ff4e6c7cf76d0fa7036","tid":1662340,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"Twitter係每日必做的任務<br />\n禁兩個制都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲同我retweet哂去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日國際新聞關香港或者抵制中國事的有：<br />\nDior (向中國道歉，承認台灣係中國）<br />\n<br />\nBlizzard(共雪禁左美國大學隊賽半年，原因係美國大學隊支持Free Hong Kong)<br />\n<br />\nDreamwork（動畫畫九段線，畫出大部分的南海係屬於中國，菲律賓嚴重抗議，荷蘭海牙仲裁已經響2016裁定九段線違反聯合國國際公約，所以Dreamwork 奶共奶到洗緊細路腦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nnba (Lebron James 鬧Morey咩都唔知就亂tweet，大家可以提出任何人都唔應該響普世價值上助紂為虐、自我審查！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你響twitter大海中唔知retweet咩好<br />\ntwitter 組整左個bot<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=3a6291a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你入    /task2</span></span><br />\n就可以搵到以上的新聞<br />\n<br />\nRetweet 加 cm ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得每日做！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你入 /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就可以見到人權法新聞同議員的tweet<br />\n<br />\n記得多謝埋人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e116026682b700a6c76eb09efe8f5713abce9bef","tid":1662340,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:07:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1642cce646ecb54c17eb6b0c553f11a664efa7ab","tid":1662340,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ab81af6d62a341146f1aba676a59abaa80785bf8","tid":1662340,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:09:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1a3180d196bba1964ba0cd1adc69d1bd34c71560","tid":1662340,"uid":154187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725b3ca0b581bf8173d6efb62f266094f2781af3","tid":1662340,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:11:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd48f5bcc5c0390d3dfc4b2450115628c68e831d","tid":1662340,"uid":195636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c194a8f0cfaeafaa6d25338810e92d4b44bc8b","tid":1662340,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T22:57:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6e25ca619e19ad5e1a5c5c3c9b403852fb073f9","tid":1662340,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T22:57:25.000Z","msg":"1020"},{"pid":"f9c22d43d6d6c5bec82c3cdc5116c85f63b44542","tid":1662340,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"